data.description:
Welcome to this move-in ready, 2-story traditional brick home. Live conveniently located, minutes away from Katy ISD schools and West Grand Parkway. Come home to an office, three spacious upstairs bedrooms, and 2.5 baths, offering a total of 1,976 square feet of comfortable living space. Step outside onto the patio deck to experience your private outdoor oasis, complete with a handy sprinkler system that keeps the lawn vibrant and lush. Indoors, discover a well-appointed kitchen and open floor plan. The home showcases a stylish combination of tile, laminate, and carpet floors, ensuring both elegance and comfort. Solar screens contribute to a cool and energy-efficient interior, while the neutral color palette provides a blank canvas for you to personalize the space to your liking. Don't let this opportunity pass by seize the chance to make this house your home today!

Renter is responsible for all utilities. No smoking allowed. There is a $35 application fee per applicant over 18 years of age. Minimum lease 1-year. Tenant must provide landlord with proof of renter's insurance within 10 days.

NON-REFUNDABLE pet deposit: $250
Pet rent: $25/month PER PET.
Dogs allowed: under 20 pounds, non-aggressive breeds only. Must submit a picture of dogs with application.
